articles.title: Dad and daughter open up on her struggles with depression and suicide attempt - AsiaOne
articles.description: A parent's love knows no bounds. Lisa Chan, 23, can vouch for this more than most. She and her 59-year-old dad Chan Heng Kay have gone through a lot in the last couple of years. In 2021, Lisa, who was struggling with depression, sat on the edge of a high-rise…
